This package is intended to take pointcloud snapshots of an objects lying on a
plane. This is usefull to create a database for model training.

./snapshot rgbd_pointcloud_topic path_to_save_dir

After launching the application, the visualizer will show what the xtion sees.
Whenever you want to take a snapshot, press "s".
The snapshot will be shown in the visualizer.
Press "s" to confirm it and it will save it to the path_to_save_dir.
If the snapshot is wrong, press "d"; the visualizer will again show you what the
xtion sees, and you will be able to take another snapshot by pressing "s".

Snapshots are RGBXYZ points.
